title: Caitlin Carmichael Attends Charmaine Blake Ultra Gold Gifting Suite
content:
View image | gettyimages.com Los Angeles, California - Eleven year old actress Caitlin Carmichael looked adorable wearing a blue dress with black heels as she stepped out to attend Charmaine Blake Ultra Gold Gifting Suite held at Mondrian Hotel on Friday, September 18th, 2015 in Los Angeles, California.
Caitlin Elizabeth Carmichael is an American child actress.
